      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect some minor oil leaks and a suspension that feels a bit loose. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading paint on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid candidate for someone willing to put in a little work to bring it back to its former glory.",
