    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2002 BMW M3, a definitive example of the E46 platform. Under the hood, the S54B32 power unit exhibits flawless compression across all six cylinders, with the high-pressure VANOS system operating silently. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, tactile throws, feeding a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The rear subframe has been thoroughly inspected and remains structurally perfect, maintaining the car's intended torsional rigidity. Suspension components retain their OEM damping characteristics and bushing integrity, providing legendary telepathic turn-in. Finished in Titan Silver Metallic, the paint depth and clear coat are consistent with a vehicle that has been exclusively climate-controlled. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Mint condition. Flawless exterior. Interior like new. No mechanical issues. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
