    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the absolute definition of 'mint.' From the gleaming, swirl-free deep metallic paint to the factory-fresh scent of the premium leather interior, every inch has been meticulously preserved. It has been strictly garage-kept under a soft cover and treated to professional ceramic coating to maintain its showroom shine. The engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of wear, and the undercarriage remains remarkably clean. All maintenance has been performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts, with a complete service history included. There are zero stone chips on the hood, no curb rash on the alloy wheels, and the cabin remains whisper-quiet. This is a collector-grade example for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
